hamhongchien)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">octobre 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I use this plugin to redirect my corporate domain name homepage to my personal blog.\nI\'m in an online business with personal branding, and I haven\'t started a company yet. I have chosen a brand domain name, great.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Looking forward seeing 404 log feature</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stasonkiev\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/052abace4b13b1d4fa5a076c21b988aa?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/052abace4b13b1d4fa5a076c21b988aa?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stasonkiev\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stasonkiev</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">octobre 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you for the plugin</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy Redirects</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5